<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<aiml>
    <category>
        <pattern>*</pattern>
        <template>
            I'm not sure how to respond to that. My name is Careerbot and I can to help you find what computer 
            science job is right for you. 
            <br/>
            <b>Please say "hello" to me and we can get started looking for your new career!</b>
        </template>
    </category>
    <category>
        <pattern>HELLO ^</pattern>
        <template>
            Hello! My name is Careerbot and I'm here to help you find what computer science job is right for you!
            <br/>
            I'm going to ask you a few questions to see what job would suit your background 
            and preferences. 
            <br/>
            Please answer the questions the best you can so I can give you the most awesome information! 
            With all that said, let's get started!
            <br/>
            <b>What is your <set name="topic">favorite course</set> from your college journey?</b>
        </template>
    </category>
    <topic name="favorite course">
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>mathclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="mathpoints">0</set></think>
                <think><set name="mathpoints"><map><name>successor</name><bot name="mathpoints"/></map></set></think>
                <think><set name="likesmath">yes</set></think>
                <think><set name="favoritecourse"><star index="2"/></set></think>
                I see you like math! <star index="2"/> in particular can be really useful for a number of jobs.
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>networkclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="netpoints">0</set></think>
                <think><set name="likesmath">unknown</set></think>
                <think><set name="netpoints"><map><name>successor</name><bot name="netpoints"/></map></set></think>
                <think><set name="favoritecourse"><star index="2"/></set></think>
                I see you like networking! <star index="2"/> in particular can be really useful for a number of jobs.
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>infosecclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="secpoints">0</set></think>
                <think><set name="likesmath">unknown</set></think>
                <think><set name="secpoints"><map><name>successor</name><bot name="secpoints"/></map></set></think>
                <think><set name="favoritecourse"><star index="2"/></set></think>
                I see you like security! <star index="2"/> in particular can be really useful for a number of jobs.
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>interactiveclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="interactpoints">0</set></think>
                <think><set name="likesmath">unknown</set></think>
                <think><set name="interactpoints"><map><name>successor</name><bot name="interactpoints"/></map></set></think>
                <think><set name="favoritecourse"><star index="2"/></set></think>
                I see you like something more interactive and with variety! <star index="2"/> in particular can be really useful for a number of jobs.
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>programmingclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="codepoints">0</set></think>
                <think><set name="likesmath">unknown</set></think>
                <think><set name="codepoints"><map><name>successor</name><bot name="codepoints"/></map></set></think>
                <think><set name="favoritecourse"><star index="2"/></set></think>
                I see you like programming! <star index="2"/> in particular can be really useful for a number of jobs.
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>noclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="interactpoints">0</set></think>
                <think><set name="likesmath">unknown</set></think>
                <think><set name="interactpoints"><map><name>successor</name><bot name="interactpoints"/></map></set></think>
                <think><set name="favoritecourse">none</set></think>
                That's unfortunate that you didn't like any of your classes! Maybe you could benefit from something more fun and free form!
                <br/>
                <b>If you really had to pick one, which class was your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>*</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="interactpoints">0</set></think>
                <think><set name="likesmath">unknown</set></think>
                <think><set name="interactpoints"><map><name>successor</name><bot name="interactpoints"/></map></set></think>
                <think><set name="favoritecourse">unknown</set></think>
                Wow I haven't heard of that before! Sounds like you've had an exciting Computer Science career!
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
    </topic>
    <topic name="least favorite">
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>mathclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="mathpoints"><map><name>predecessor</name><bot name="mathpoints"/></map></set></think>
                I can understand that! Classes like <star index="2"/> can be offputting for a number of reasons. I'm glad you go through it though!
                <br/>
                <b>Now that I got what your favorites are, what are some <set name="topic">hobbies</set> you have?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>networkclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="netpoints"><map><name>predecessor</name><bot name="netpoints"/></map></set></think>
                    I can understand that! Classes like <star index="2"/> can be offputting for a number of reasons. I'm glad you go through it though!
                    <br/>
                <condition name="likesmath">
                    <li value="yes">
                        I was going to ask you next what feelings you had about math, but since you like <get name="favoritecourse"/> I think I know the answer to that! 
                        <br/> 
                        <b>Instead, what are some <set name="topic">hobbies</set> you have?</b>
                    </li>
                    <li value="unknown">
                        Next up, I wanted to ask you how much you like <set name="topic">math</set>. Thought it is a very prominent in computer science,
                        it doesn't always fit well with everyone. 
                        <br/>
                        <b>With that said, do you enjoy math?</b>
                    </li>
                </condition>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>infosecclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="secpoints"><map><name>predecessor</name><bot name="secpoints"/></map></set></think>
                I can understand that! Classes like <star index="2"/> can be offputting for a number of reasons. I'm glad you go through it though!
                <br/>
                <b>Now that I got what your favorites are, what are some <set name="topic">hobbies</set> you have?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>interactiveclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="interactpoints"><map><name>predecessor</name><bot name="interactpoints"/></map></set></think>
                I can understand that! Some broad classes like <star index="2"/> can be offputting for a number of reasons. I'm glad you go through it though!
                <br/>
                <b>Now that I got what your favorites are, what are some <set name="topic">hobbies</set> you have?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>programmingclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name="codepoints"><map><name>predecessor</name><bot name="codepoints"/></map></set></think>
                I can understand that! Classes like <star index="2"/> can be offputting for a number of reasons. I'm glad you go through it though!
                <br/>
                <b>Now that I got what your favorites are, what are some <set name="topic">hobbies</set> you have?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>*</pattern>
            <template>
                Even though that class don't ring a bell for me, It still sounds like a hassel to deal with!
                <br/>
                <b>Now that I got what your favorites are, what are some <set name="topic">hobbies</set> you have?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
    </topic>
    <topic name="hobbies">
    </topic>
    <category>
        <pattern>HI ^</pattern>
        <template><srai>HELLO *</srai></template>
    </category>
    <category>
        <pattern># <set>positivebeforenoun</set> ^ MATH ^</pattern>
        <template>I'm glad you <star index="2"/> math! It's fantastic!</template>
    </category>
    <category>
        <pattern># MATH ^ <set>positiveafternoun</set> ^</pattern>
        <template>I'm glad you think math <person><star index="2"/></person> <star index="3"/>! It is really great!</template>
    </category>
    <category>
        <pattern>^ I * ^ MATH ^</pattern>
        <template>I'm sorry to hear you <star index="2"/> math! It's fantastic!</template>
    </category>
</aiml>
